What a bugger! Mom and I got rejected on the door at Snaxx at Berghain in Berlin. 
So we straight went with our outfits to the musical “Rock of ages!” 

Doesn’t my mom look like a damn rockstar? 🤩 

I took my parents yesterday to the musical “Rock of Ages” in Munich as a gift for my dads 60th birthday two weeks ago! 

And yes, we dressed up appropriate!😜 

The talent of this musical was Incredible and totally could compete with the original broadway one! 

We loved it and could sing along to every song! ☺️
I’m a little bit jealous of this music generation! 
So much fun! 

(Dad was Camera shy)

„Hey sexy, I saw you are in Berlin!“ 🫠

Shocking to see how many people are really thinking I’m in Berlin and have my mom join me for biggest gay sex fetish party at Berghain because of my most recent post. How can some not get THIS level of irony? 🙄🤯🤣 

„Hey mom can you wait around that married guy in leather as long im having fun on drugs in the sling area down there? See you later!“ 🤣
